  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Sixty day single arm trial examining self-report and remote dermatology assessment of
      cosmetic skin health after daily 10-20 minute sessions with an infrared light therapy device
      (the Joovv Mini)
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
